@node Win GCC Installation, , Win GCC Files, GCC Windows
@subsubsection Installation

@itemize @bullet
@item
Unzip the compiled libraries into the same folder where you unzipped
Crystal Space.

@item
Unzip NASM somwhere.

@item
Run the Cygwin full.exe installer.

@item
To use GCC and NASM you need to make sure you have the appropriate bin
directories in your PATH. Here's my own PATH as an example:
@example
SET PATH=C:\Cygnus\cygwin-b20\H-i586-cygwin32\bin;C:\nasm\bin\win32;%PATH%
@end example

@item
Now just CD to your Crystal Space directory, run make and follow the
instructions.
@end itemize
